chart.name: Memory Used %
chart.programText:
A = data('signalfx.usedmemory').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('memory.available_mbytes').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A / (A + B) * 100).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Disk I/O Ops
chart.programText:
H = data('logicaldisk.disk_reads_sec', filter=filter('instance', '_total')).sum().publish(label='H')
I = data('logicaldisk.disk_writes_sec', filter=filter('instance', '_total')).sum().publish(label='I')

chart.name: Network Errors
chart.programText:
A = data('network_interface.packets_received_errors').sum(by=['host']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('network_interface.packets_outbound_errors').sum(by=['host']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
D = (A + B).sum().publish(label='D')

chart.name: Total Disk Space
chart.programText:
A = data('logicaldisk.free_megabytes', filter=filter('instance', '_total')).sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('logicaldisk.pct_free_space', filter=filter('instance', '_total')).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A / (B/100)).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (C - A).sum().publish(label='D')

chart.name: Disk Read/Write Duration (ms)
chart.programText:
A = data('physicaldisk.avg_disk_sec_read.Duration-Mean-us', filter=(not filter('instance', '_total'))).sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('physicaldisk.avg_disk_sec_write.Duration-Mean-us', filter=(not filter('instance', '_total'))).sum().publish(label='B')

chart.name: Disk Used %
chart.programText:
A = data('logicaldisk.pct_free_space', filter=(not filter('instance', '_total'))).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (100 - A).publish(label='B')

chart.name: CPU %
chart.programText:
A = data('processor.pct_processor_time').mean(by=['host']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).max().publish(label='B')
C = (A).min().publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='E')
F = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='F')

chart.name: Total Network Errors
chart.programText:
A = data('network_interface.packets_received_errors').sum(by=['host']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('network_interface.packets_outbound_errors').sum(by=['host']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
D = (A + B).sum().publish(label='D')

chart.name: Memory Used %
chart.programText:
A = data('memory.available_mbytes').sum(by=['host']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('signalfx.usedmemory').sum(by=['host']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
D = (A / (A + B) * 100).publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = (D).min().publish(label='E')
F = (D).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='F')
G = (D).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='G')
H = (D).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='H')
I = (D).max().publish(label='I')
